      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * Programming</b>\n</p><p>This is about general purpose <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Computer_programming\">programming</a> topics with focus on computer chess - <a href=\"/Languages\" title=\"Languages\">programming languages</a>, <a href=\"/Algorithms\" title=\"Algorithms\">algorithms</a>, <a href=\"/Data\" title=\"Data\">data</a> and various optimization techniques and standards.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Programming_Topics\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Programming Topics</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Basics\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Basics</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Parallelism\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Parallelism</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Misc_Programming\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc Programming</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#GUI_Programming\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">GUI Programming</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Bug_Hunting\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Bug Hunting</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Optimization\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Optimization</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Standards\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Standards</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#Position\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Position</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#Games\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Games</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#Protocols\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Protocols</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-12\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-13\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-14\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-15\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">8</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-16\"><a href=\"#Computation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">8.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Computation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-17\"><a href=\"#Paradigms\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">8.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Paradigms</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-18\"><a href=\"#Misc\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">8.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-19\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">9</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Programming_Topics\">Programming Topics</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Programming&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Programming Topics\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Basics\"><span id=\"Basics\"